VL  - 23
IS  - 4
PB  - Academy of Management
N2  - The change in 24 structural and strategy making variables over time is analyzed by a study of 26 companies. Organizations were found to resist reversals in the direction of change in strategy and structure. Two extremes were demonstrated: periods of momentum in which little or no trend is reversed and dramatic periods of revolution in which a very great many trends are reversed.
AB  - The change in 24 structural and strategy making variables over time is analyzed by a study of 26 companies. Organizations were found to resist reversals in the direction of change in strategy and structure. Two extremes were demonstrated: periods of momentum in which little or no trend is reversed and dramatic periods of revolution in which a very great many trends are reversed.
